cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.SY 

The paper is focused on machine learning architecture and algorithms, specifically on cloning the functionality of black-box models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves active learning algorithms, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). As the paper deals with security and privacy concerns, it could also be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper mentions the use of complex analog circuits and mechanical systems, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SY (Systems and Control), respectively.
